<div class="container-self">
  <h3>Mixxt Recognize</h3>
  <p><strong>Mixxt Recognize</strong> is a beta feature that uses <%= link_to "AudD Music Recogniton Api", "https://audd.io/"  %>.</p>
  <p>Please follow these steps to use Mixxt Recognize:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><%= link_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path %> to your Mixxt account or <%= link_to "Sign up",  new_user_registration_path %> if you do not have an account yet.</li>
    <li>Get your own Audd API key <%= link_to "here", "https://t.me/auddbot?start=api." %>. <i>You will need to use Telegram for that.</i> </li>
    <li>Enter the Audd Key on your<% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "profile page", edit_user_path(current_user) %>
      <% else %>
        profile page
      <% end %> .</li>
    <li>Now you will see a <strong>Recognize</strong> button on <%= link_to "Mixxt home page", root_path %>.</li>
    <%= link_to "Home", root_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
  </ul>
</div>